item.title: CVE-2019-9132|2024-08-04T21:38:46.549Z -- kakao -- kakaotalk%20windows%20pc%20messenger
item.description: Remote code execution vulnerability exists in KaKaoTalk PC messenger when user clicks specially crafted link in the message window. This affects KaKaoTalk windows version 2.7.5.2024 or lower.
